{"tid":2193964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"03年港府：現行「煽動罪行」涵義太闊，建議大幅度收窄。","createTime":"2020-09-08T08:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T09:14:26.000Z","uid":219007,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a38356a5236c54ac108fe26af5e15563802053d6","tid":2193964,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:26:24.000Z","msg":"03年政府諮詢23條時候指現時《刑事罪行條例》9及10條 （告快必個幾條）係涵義太闊，建議大幅度收窄。<br />\n<br />\nBackup<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/info/basiclaw23_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fbasiclaw23_c.pdf&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=9c1d02fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/info/basiclaw23_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewQtQNt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FewQtQNt.png&h=6663bac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦以普通法原則下解釋何謂「煽動」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kj18QNV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKj18QNV.png&h=dce4d332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府舉例指：參與遊行示威時，煽動他人作出刑事行為，如暴力或燒毁汽車。 <span class=\"red\"><strong>該行為不是屬於煽動叛亂</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2kp8Aq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2kp8Aq.png&h=04747e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以政府鳩噏話23條立法等建議內容完全符合國際人權公約<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pjOfvO5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpjOfvO5.png&h=3b27a311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃毓民解釋廿三條法律背景同當年諮詢過程<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C53CfWflEu8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC53CfWflEu8&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=20d15e8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C53CfWflEu8</a><br />\n二十三條立法諮詢文件對「煽動」定義講得好清楚 黃毓民 毓民踩場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">記者朋友，你哋去咗邊</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6c434ea30969d975549811b3cd4a51402d8ef8","tid":2193964,"uid":25794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:28:12.000Z","msg":"玩死班人咩, 又要搵返出黎delete<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de2b2e17630d70d815aea8ae135c2263e04aea2","tid":2193964,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01f8ac51e63b98daa8ab4ec892890948b0d9e12","tid":2193964,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3128569bc3bdce32ffc07954a5c88ed40c6a24","tid":2193964,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:31:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce4213cccb0fb869cc62621d37f06f1acb75cfb5","tid":2193964,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbec28113fd6b1ba662d38c9204654878914dac","tid":2193964,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:32:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bdd336b2326421980011cc23268263dd085